### Hi I'm Darkun7 <img src="https://media.giphy.com/media/hvRJCLFzcasrR4ia7z/giphy.gif" width="25px">
Hi, I'm [Hartawan Bahari M](https://kulacino.my.id/). I hold a degree in **Information Systems** from the **University of Jember** and am currently pursuing a degree in **Informatics** at **Institut Teknologi Sepuluh Nopember (ITS)** in Surabaya, Indonesia, focusing my research on **Information Security**. My interests include Back-end Development, Cloud Computing, and Machine Learning. 

Previously, I worked as a full-time **Fullstack Developer** at [Smartjen](https://www.smartjen.com), utilizing the Laravel and Vue stack, and handled machine learning tasks as part of the **R&D** team.
